Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积在身上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为已经等了整整两小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为才两点左右呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算才两点 也迟到一小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.58,0:00:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 抱歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:00:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 还记得我的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是要问你 还记得我的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.39,0:01:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.29,0:01:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家是女孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.96,0:01:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 真的要感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做着一个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个每天都做的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有尽头的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被染成红色的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛要遮盖夕阳的天空的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个正在哭泣的孩童
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少想拭去他流出的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 却连手也举不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.71,0:03:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪水划过脸颊 渗入雪中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能静静地看着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好无助 好悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请不要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为约定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这言语是谁说的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦渐渐被染成其它颜色…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 约定好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服 制服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的已经没有时间了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服 制服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早的就在吵什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哦 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上要好好说一声「早上好」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 祐一 知道我的制服在哪儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是秋子阿姨拿去洗了吗 我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的设计啊 这套制服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了哦 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还有点湿湿的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放到被炉里马上就会干的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做的话 会变得皱巴巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是冬季生活的常识哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.59,0:05:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要这样的生活常识呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不还是寒假中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但我还有社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我还是部长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的确也有说过练习什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 田径部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪是田径部的部长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是湿湿的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赶快一些可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当然不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这个时间了 现在去还来得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出一百米七秒跑完的速度就来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这刷新世界纪录了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨 这口锅是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我走了咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.82,0:06:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过会儿能不能带我参观一下这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我完全没有问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点小事没什么 我走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心汽车哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很累吧 累了的话休息一下也没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有男孩子在还真是帮了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我母亲的妹妹 水濑秋子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是名雪的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经到那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小的时候 我经常来这座城市游玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和名雪以及秋子阿姨 则是阔别七年后的再会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么祐一 我来带你参观这个城市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 你还是一点都没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是我一点都没成长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地让你陪着真抱歉了 才刚刚回到家的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赶快适应这个城市才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为祐一以后要一直生活在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 一直呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道会不会一直生活在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但至少高中毕业前会一直生活在这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（1832 拖车到黑石署报到）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（防滑砂）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们的学校哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近以前是麦田吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这边是新校舍 那边是旧校舍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还在假期 学生还真多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为还有补习和社团等等各种活动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从明天开始我也将成为这里的学生了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐祐理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找你好久了 舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在给小狗喂食了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在抚摸而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是医院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就有了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太想和那地方扯上关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一很怕去医院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会喜欢医院的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,75)\fs57}冷吗 栞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,75)\fs57}还好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.96,0:09:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近还真是变得热闹了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我常常在对面的商店街买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香里 北川君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:10:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同班同学 香里可是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见呢 水濑也在约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫也在 我们只不过是偶然遇到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你别让偶然遇到的家伙拿这么多东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是相泽祐一 是我的表哥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美坂香里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我香里就行了 相泽君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责给她提行李的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁是提行李的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川君 帮我拿一下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.85,0:10:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是提行李的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是的 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 作为友好的表示
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我买的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说这么小气的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说在前面 不要对香里出手 香里是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是同班同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 明天学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少让我做男朋友候补吧 香里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香里小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们俩和我坐得很近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个山丘一点都没变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 只是过去的事情记不太清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然感觉发生过很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.31,0:11:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大多忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连是不是真的喜欢这个城市也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能因为当时还小 现在并没有怀念之类的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的许多事情一定会慢慢想起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也希望祐一能够喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来吧～小狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来 过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了 会被咬的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是那么喜欢动物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来～过来～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是野生的狐狸吧 哪会那么容易亲近人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢 这个山丘上的狐狸是很特别的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有个古老的传说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么传说？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该去买晚饭的材料了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里等你好了 进去好像会迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 有我在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为有你在才担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你在这里等着 不可以走开哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 我站在这里一动不动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起以前也有过相似的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 快去快回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年前 我也看过这样的景色吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快闪开 快闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕 快闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为速度太快了没能避开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶跑得才没那么快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 请别谦虚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 有话等会儿再说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么安不安全的 我连发生了什么都不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶正被人追呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.29,0:14:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被发现和偶在一起 你也会有危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经决定要点的菜了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会儿再点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙在追你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你那个纸袋有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完 完全没有一点关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是个很善良的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不可貌相哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他穿着围裙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是烤鲷鱼烧的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么鲷鱼烧大叔要来追你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个卖鲷鱼烧的地方偶很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点了很多的时候都还很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想付钱的时候 却发现钱包不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在想该怎么办的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁边来了一只想要偷吃鲷鱼烧的小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.98,0:15:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔一副凶相毕露的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是偶也吓了一跳 然后就逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话 完全是你单方面的错咯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕 还有别的原因嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来话长了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缘由极其复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子实在太饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么听都是你的不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.60,0:16:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶明天会好好地去付钱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱我来付 现在马上去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 能得到原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然鲷鱼烧还是刚烧好的最美味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变胖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶才不在乎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我监督你把剩下的全吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:16:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕 别学人家的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你从刚才开始就一直在用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕 才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背后的翅膀是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翅膀？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有翅膀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你背后的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背后？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕 看不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头时身体别动就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊 有翅膀耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点察觉到了 难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个怪人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕 才没有这回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就此告别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要好好还钱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶叫月宫亚由 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相泽祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一君？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.61,0:18:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是还能见面就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然咯 你这么说话小心不还你钱了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下次再见了 约定好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉 我从刚才就一直在道歉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等了你半个钟头的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.93,0:19:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 昨天我也迟到了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搬家的行李都送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来光靠今天是收拾不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先找个闹钟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 把我的借你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要几个好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.75,0:19:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个就够
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢哪个随便挑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有收集的兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有这回事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一的话 推荐这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上要说「晚安」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:19:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新城市的新生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的冬季的一天慢慢过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在半梦半醒之际 一个少女的身影浮现在脑海里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不清楚那是谁的情况下 我睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话太阳要下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈让我帮忙去买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一说好帮拿东西的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太冷了 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就要扎千针
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且现在增量期间要扎千五百针
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一也进去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里等你好了 进去好像会迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 有我在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.00,0:21:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为有你在才担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了 你在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.76,0:21:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 为什么要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.41,0:21:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.04,0:21:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫相泽祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓也是亚由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是被欺负了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄妹吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 先离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.06,0:21:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 亚由亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.96,0:21:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是亚由亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么果酱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.04,0:23:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.16,0:23:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相泽祐一 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的成同班了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.05,0:23:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:23:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿还要去道歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.23,0:24:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 刚才好像有走过这条路？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.97,0:24:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像以前一样拉钩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.81,0:24:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.35,0:24:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
